    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you can expect some minor oil leaks and a suspension that feels a bit loose. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional car at a lower price point who doesn't mind performing some cosmetic or minor mechanical upkeep.",
