    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a dependable vehicle that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin!",
