    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in wonderful condition, ready for its next owner. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only the minor, expected signs of road use that come with careful driving. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather seats are supple and free of tears, and all electronic features\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, it is sound and has been serviced at regular intervals, with a complete folder of maintenance records available for review. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts crisply, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. This is a reliable, high-quality car that offers a premium driving experience for a discerning buyer who values a well-documented history.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
