    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for my awesome car! It's in really solid condition and has been super reliable for me. It drives like a dream and is perfect for anyone looking for a dependable, well-maintained ride that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have! Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 32500.0,
