    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a driver-focused example of BMW\u2019s iconic S54-powered platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies, paired with a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable locking differential. This unit has been maintained with mechanical longevity in mind; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the dual-VANOS system remains within factory tolerances. Suspension kinematics are sharp, utilizing a refreshed bushing set to maintain the chassis' high-speed stability and turn-in precision. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust, providing the visceral analog feedback sought by purists.",
